                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10245" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1175</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">204 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冰与火的淬炼--中诚信集团滑雪产业的创业发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ice and Fire--CCX Group’s Skiing Industry&#39;s Entrepreneurial Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘学元，王建军，EricMa，何承骋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中诚信集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；企业社会责任；创业管理；商业模式创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Entrepreneurship; Corporate Social Responsibility; Entrepreneurial Management; Business Model Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025年2月14日晚，第九届亚洲冬季运动会在哈尔滨圆满落下帷幕。作为2022年北京冬奥会后我国首个国际级冰雪体育赛事，亚冬会的举办标志着中国冰雪经济正从规模扩张阶段向质量效益提升阶段加速迈进。中国滑雪产业最早起步于上世纪八十年代的黑龙江省亚布力，经过近40年的发展，目前已经进入快速成长与发展阶段。然而，其发展之路并非坦途，长期面临着季节性依赖突出、前期投入高昂且回报周期漫长、运营模式单一化、自然条件制约与区域市场分化等多重挑战，这些问题如同枷锁，制约着产业的进一步腾飞。中诚信作为一家构建起丰富信用产品矩阵、拥有完整信用产业链条的综合性信用产业集团，其涉足滑雪产业的创业实践具有独特研究价值。对中诚信滑雪产业展开深度案例分析，不仅能细致探析中国滑雪产业从萌芽起步到艰难创业、逐步发展的曲折历程，更能通过其在滑雪产业发展困境中实施的商业模式创新，洞察企业如何在逆境中突破困局。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On the evening of February 14, 2025, the 9th Asian Winter Games concluded successfully in Harbin. As China&#39;s first international ice and snow sports event following the Beijing Winter Olympics, the Games marked the accelerated shift of China&#39;s ice and snow economy from a scale-driven expansion phase to one focused on quality and efficiency.
China&#39;s ice and snow industry first took root in Yabuli, Heilongjiang Province, in the 1980s. After nearly four decades of development, it has now entered a stage of rapid growth. However, its path has been far from smooth, long facing challenges such as prominent seasonal dependence, high upfront investment with lengthy return cycles, single-dimensional operation models, natural condition constraints, and regional market fragmentation—issues that have long hindered the industry&#39;s further advancement.
As a comprehensive credit industry group with a rich portfolio of credit products and a complete credit industry chain, China Chengxin International Group&#39;s (CCXI) foray into the skiing industry offers unique research value. A deep case analysis of CCXI&#39;s skiing operations not only allows for a meticulous exploration of the tortuous journey of China&#39;s ice and snow industry from its embryonic stage to its arduous entrepreneurial development but also reveals how enterprises can break through adversity through business model innovations amid the sector&#39;s developmental challenges.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《创新管理》、《商业伦理与社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业管理、创业机会识别、企业社会责任、商业模式创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
